                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-date&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;&gt;&lt;a class=&quot;comment-link&quot; href=&quot;#comment8342672_978094&quot;&gt;&lt;span title=&quot;2011-08-09 01:43:50Z, License: CC BY-SA 3.0&quot; class=&quot;relativetime-clean&quot;&gt;Aug 9, 2011 at 1:43&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;
            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;I think the success and breadth of adoption (and abuse) of the protocols speaks to the value of the robustness principle.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/114986/caskey&quot; title=&quot;11,745 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;caskey&lt;/a&gt;
