            &lt;/div&gt;

            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec9.html#sec9.5&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noreferrer&quot;&gt;Section 9.5&lt;/a&gt;, &quot;POST&quot;, also doesn&apos;t mention request bodies, so this logic is flawed.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;/users/967077/carluva&quot; title=&quot;440 reputation&quot; class=&quot;comment-user&quot;&gt;CarLuva&lt;/a&gt;
