                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;This example is pointless because usually when people are going to add body to &lt;code&gt;GET&lt;/code&gt; requests, it&apos;s because their own custom server are able to handle it. The question thus is whether the other &quot;moving parts&quot; (browsers, caches, etc) will work properly.&lt;/span&gt;

