                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;You should just use POST. If there is a method name in the url, you are violating the fundamental rest design. This is RPC, use POST.&lt;/span&gt;

              &lt;div class=&quot;d-inline-flex ai-center&quot;&gt;
