            &lt;div class=&quot;comment-body js-comment-edit-hide&quot;&gt;

                &lt;span class=&quot;comment-copy&quot;&gt;I don&apos;t think that is a big deal, we have more problems during development with RESTful url (i.e. orders/1). As for me, something wrong with Get method, it&apos;s incompatible with OOP. And who care how url is look like :) But with message based approach we can create stable remote interface and it&apos;s really important. P.S. it&apos;s not RPC, it&apos;s message based&lt;/span&gt;

